Gorp Bars
Gram

1 cup light corn syrup
1/2 cup light or dark brown sugar (packed)
1/4 teaspoon salt
1 1/2 cup peanut butter (chunky optional)
1 teaspoon vanilla
1 cup non-fat dry milk
1 cup raisins
2 cups granola
6 ounces chocolate chips
1 cup of optional ingredients

Line 13x9" pan with wax paper
In large or medium saucepan, combine sugar, syrup & salt. Bring to boil over high heat. (1 1/2 to 2 minutes)
Stir in peanut butter
Remove from heat
Stir in vanilla
Stir in remaining ingredients
Press mixture into 13x9" pan
Refrigerate for 30 minutes
Cut into bars
Refrigerate

Will withstand many substitutions
